headline.main: NHL GMs to Talk Video Review, Concussion Protocol at Meeting
headline.print_headline: NHL GMs to Talk Video Review, Concussion Protocol at Meeting

lead_paragraph: When a collision knocked off Mike Smith's mask, the Arizona Coyotes goaltender was less than pleased upon being told a few minutes later he had to leave the game.
